## Do Not Claim

- Do not claim Telos has solved any grand challenge in this registry.
- Do not claim a subproblem receipt solves the parent frontier problem.
- Do not promote arXiv, web, or institutional pages from `SOURCE_LEAD` to truth.
- Do not make clinical or safety claims without domain-appropriate review.
- Do not use `PROMOTED_LAW` until independent proof, reproduction, and review exist.
